snippet.title: Game & Watch - Oil Panic (OP-51) (c)1982 Nintendo (with case artwork) [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
This is Oil Panic, part of the Nintendo's Game & Watch series, running in MAME.  Emulation is by algestam.  This one was emulated in MAME 0.205, and a video from 2018 exists on the channel, this however is a fresh upload with updated artwork to better represent the current state.

Game & Watch artwork for MAME was done by DarthMarino (more recently emulated units) and hydef (units emulated before 2020)
https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY  DarthMarino 
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1WLKcvynl0ky2mRL1UacA9yaiMTnNs4x5 hydef
